to catch the Devil.

525
00:40:04,100 --> 00:40:06,739
Man doesn't possess
such power over him.

526
00:40:06,940 --> 00:40:10,171
Don't you understand,
this is done by a man?

527
00:40:13,380 --> 00:40:16,019
We have to come up
with a clever plan

528
00:40:16,340 --> 00:40:20,015
to catch this murderer
and gold robber.

529
00:40:21,500 --> 00:40:22,774
We have to find a way

530
00:40:22,980 --> 00:40:25,733
how to drive that sucky Stig
out of town for good.

531
00:40:25,940 --> 00:40:27,851
Before he takes away our mom.

532
00:40:28,060 --> 00:40:31,291
I think we should scare
that Stig properly.

533
00:40:31,500 --> 00:40:34,014
He doesn't look like a guy
who's afraid of anything.

534
00:40:34,340 --> 00:40:37,571
If he met the real White Lady
at the castle tonight

535
00:40:37,780 --> 00:40:39,691
then I bet he would be scared.

536
00:40:39,940 --> 00:40:41,771
Where do we get the White Lady?

537
00:40:41,980 --> 00:40:45,052
I saw that Stig has a camera
with Wifi.

538
00:40:45,660 --> 00:40:49,050
He sends all the pictures
over internet to his hard drive.

539
00:40:49,260 --> 00:40:50,249
So?

540
00:40:51,020 --> 00:40:52,692
Same time that he's
photographing the castle,

541
00:40:52,900 --> 00:40:55,289
me and Markus
will go to his room.

542
00:40:55,580 --> 00:40:58,333
I'll hack his computer and leave
him some ghost photos.

543
00:40:58,620 --> 00:41:01,498
Karl, dad told you,
no more hacking.

544
00:41:01,700 --> 00:41:04,339
You've had enough trouble
because of this already.

545
00:41:05,420 --> 00:41:07,058
But if it's for the sake of justice?

546
00:41:07,300 --> 00:41:09,894
What if that sucky Stig really
woos my Mom

547
00:41:10,100 --> 00:41:11,738
and takes her away for good?

548
00:41:13,220 --> 00:41:15,939
All right, but this is
the very last time.

549
00:41:20,660 --> 00:41:21,695
Teacher!

550
00:41:21,900 --> 00:41:24,539
Teacher, I managed to create gold!
- Show me.

551
00:41:29,500 --> 00:41:32,014
The purest gold that
I have ever seen.

552
00:41:32,260 --> 00:41:34,091
Do you remember the whole process? 
- Yes.

553
00:41:34,340 --> 00:41:38,015
Write it all down so it remains
on the record forever.

554
00:42:07,100 --> 00:42:09,694
Give me the gold recipe!

555
00:42:09,900 --> 00:42:11,891
So you were the one
who killed all those monks?

556
00:42:12,100 --> 00:42:14,898
That secret you shall take
to your grave.

557
00:42:21,060 --> 00:42:26,976
You're the one who robbed formulas
and recipes for making gold.

558
00:42:28,100 --> 00:42:32,616
Take him to the torture chamber,
he'll start talking.

559
00:42:34,740 --> 00:42:37,891
Berit, what do you think if there's
any truth to this White Lady's tale?

560
00:42:38,100 --> 00:42:40,819
I believe that every legend
is based on something.

561
00:42:41,060 --> 00:42:44,735
White Lady or that young girl was really
buried somewhere within these walls?

562
00:42:45,100 --> 00:42:46,613
I'm certain of it.

563
00:42:46,860 --> 00:42:48,373
It was discovered that a girl dressed
as a boy had entered the castle

564
00:42:51,100 --> 00:42:53,170
having an affair with
one of the monks

565
00:42:53,420 --> 00:42:55,775
and these days it was punishable
by death.

566
00:42:56,580 --> 00:42:57,854
Sad story.

567
00:43:00,300 --> 00:43:03,212
I wouldn't be surprised if after this
a young girl's ghost would

568
00:43:03,500 --> 00:43:06,458
haunt this place, appearing
on the window every year.

569
00:43:07,580 --> 00:43:09,491
May I have a look? 
- No.

570
00:43:10,540 --> 00:43:12,098
Of course you can.

571
00:43:12,860 --> 00:43:13,849
Over here.

572
00:43:22,140 --> 00:43:23,414
Come!

573
00:43:40,340 --> 00:43:42,296
Can you? 
- Yes.

574
00:43:57,900 --> 00:43:59,253
Look.

575
00:43:59,780 --> 00:44:01,816
These are the files he is
photographing right now.

576
00:44:02,380 --> 00:44:04,291
Photoshop some ghouls here.
